 guy, but c'mon, you think on a Wednesday night we need a breath mint guy handing us paper towels?!?  I don't think so.  As a matter of fact, let's do away with this ridiculous fixture once and for all.  You women don't have to deal with a matronly old bag sitting there on a stool, collecting tips for perfume samples and spare pads, do you?  I didn't think so.  This is nothing a decent vending machine couldn't handle.  Plus I feel sorry for the guy -- I mean, at least he's not a human signpost out in the sun, but what a crap job. I'll be back here for more free poker, because its got more nipples showing than Bullshooters [http://www.yelp.com/biz/bull-shooters-inc-phoenix#hrid:bYK0DGz8LSGZfZCdkEjX8g ], and because the boobies I see are not on old Native dudes like at Wild Bill's  [ http://www.yelp.com/biz/wild-bills-saloon-phoenix#hrid:sCd6p_CiAVonqLF0N-8PmA ]

